  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nProjects that `require` node modules in migrations work on 3.2.5 but do not work on 3.3.0.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nWith testrpc running, in a new directory:\r\n```\r\ntruffle init\r\nnpm init -f\r\nnpm install --save assert\r\necho -e \"var assert = require('assert')\\n$(cat ./migrations/2_deploy_contracts.js)\" > ./migrations/2_deploy_contracts.js\r\ntruffle test\r\n```\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe tests should run as expected. Output with Truffle 3.2.5:\r\n```\r\n truffle test\r\nCompiling ./contracts/ConvertLib.sol...\r\nCompiling ./contracts/MetaCoin.sol...\r\nCompiling ./contracts/Migrations.sol...\r\nCompiling ./test/TestMetacoin.sol...\r\nCompiling truffle/Assert.sol...\r\nCompiling truffle/DeployedAddresses.sol...\r\n\r\n\r\n  TestMetacoin\r\n    ✓ testInitialBalanceUsingDeployedContract (124ms)\r\n    ✓ testInitialBalanceWithNewMetaCoin (120ms)\r\n\r\n  Contract: MetaCoin\r\n    ✓ should put 10000 MetaCoin in the first account (42ms)\r\n    ✓ should call a function that depends on a linked library (115ms)\r\n    ✓ should send coin correctly (216ms)\r\n\r\n\r\n  5 passing (1s)\r\n```\r\n## Actual Results\r\n```\r\nCompiling ./contracts/ConvertLib.sol...\r\nCompiling ./contracts/MetaCoin.sol...\r\nCompiling ./contracts/Migrations.sol...\r\nCompiling ./test/TestMetacoin.sol...\r\nCompiling truffle/Assert.sol...\r\nCompiling truffle/DeployedAddresses.sol...\r\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v7.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:85871\r\n            return !(function webpackMissingModule() { var e = new Error(\"Cannot find module \\\".\\\"\"); e.code = 'MODULE_NOT_FOUND'; throw e; }());\r\n                                                                                                                                   ^\r\n\r\nError: Cannot find module \".\"\r\n    at webpackMissingModule (~/.nvm/versions/node/v7.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:85871:64)\r\n    at require (~/.nvm/versions/node/v7.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:85871:142)\r\n    at ~/truffle-issue/migrations/2_deploy_contracts.js:1:14\r\n    at ContextifyScript.Script.runInContext (vm.js:37:29)\r\n    at ContextifyScript.Script.runInNewContext (vm.js:43:15)\r\n    at ~/.nvm/versions/node/v7.4.0/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:85890:14\r\n    at tryToString (fs.js:426:3)\r\n    at FSReqWrap.readFileAfterClose [as oncomplete] (fs.js:413:12)\r\n```\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: OSX El Capitan\r\n* Truffle version: 3.3.0\r\n* Ethereum client: Testrpc v4.0.0\r\n* node version: 7.4\r\n* npm version: 4.0.5\r\n",
